Working area; Globally.

Responsible for the global relationship with one the top 3 international carriers:
· Commercially qualify, respond to and proactively follow up on all clients’ enquiries;
· Increase awareness of Expereo capabilities providing training and presentations to clients;
· Act as focal point for clients’ RFI’s, RFP’s, orders, escalations etc;
· Set the pace with clients and liaise with internal (pre- and post-sales) departments while managing client’s expectations;
· Participate in various project teams in order to support the business.
- Guide and support team members in several regions globally
